\arccos\in [0,\pi)
w(x) = Ax^2 - Bx^4, \quad A,B > 0
\varphi = \arccos\left(\rho A^{-2/3}\right),\quad \rho < 0\mbox{ fixed}.
b = \sqrt{\frac{2A}{3B}}\cos{\frac{\varphi}{3}}
\beta = \sqrt{\frac{A}{2}}\sin{\frac{\varphi}{3}} - \sqrt{\frac{A}{6B}}\cos{\frac{\varphi}{3}}.
A
 w(b) = w(\beta) + (b - \beta + 1)c, \quad c>0 \mbox{ is fixed.} 
